ffdc678b692c01b3d616b171b4f7cbdd5c7","tid":2490150,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"見過好多唔戴BRA既女<br />\n多數著最少2件衫  <br />\n佢地會弓起條腰盡量唔頂起件衫<br />\n而且多數都唔係話大波<br />\n一係就將個棉花扣係件衫度 唔突點就得"},{"pid":"ae2b8fb407014cca6aa36873520ccab0a6b8ebf8","tid":2490150,"uid":83912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d36f1ee7d9dbe20239644d099be2fd55d434f0e","tid":2490150,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"近一兩年成日見到，成個外型係加分嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"香港都多左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國絲表示冇戴好耐<br />\nBra 真心勁難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但返香港真係淆淆地<br />\n怕左啲麻甩廢中廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}